{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1354,"text":"Technology has brought us so much:"},{"time":4489,"text":"the moon landing, the Internet,"},{"time":6508,"text":"the ability to sequence the human genome."},{"time":9133,"text":"But it also taps into a lot of our deepest fears,"},{"time":12857,"text":"and about 30 years ago,"},{"time":14713,"text":"the culture critic Neil Postman wrote a book"},{"time":17266,"text":"called \"Amusing Ourselves to Death,\""},{"time":19381,"text":"which lays this out really brilliantly."},{"time":22140,"text":"And here's what he said,"},{"time":23790,"text":"comparing the dystopian visions"},{"time":26053,"text":"of George Orwell and Aldous Huxley."},{"time":29626,"text":"He said, Orwell feared we would become"},{"time":32752,"text":"a captive culture."},{"time":35000,"text":"Huxley feared we would become a trivial culture."},{"time":38752,"text":"Orwell feared the truth would be"},{"time":40897,"text":"concealed from us,"},{"time":42820,"text":"and Huxley feared we would be drowned"},{"time":45010,"text":"in a sea of irrelevance."},{"time":47703,"text":"In a nutshell, it's a choice between"},{"time":49873,"text":"Big Brother watching you"},{"time":52473,"text":"and you watching Big Brother."},{"time":54969,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":56900,"text":"But it doesn't have to be this way."},{"time":58634,"text":"We are not passive consumers\nof data and technology."},{"time":61970,"text":"We shape the role it plays in our lives"},{"time":64373,"text":"and the way we make meaning from it,"},{"time":66503,"text":"but to do that,"},{"time":68106,"text":"we have to pay as much attention to how we think"},{"time":71619,"text":"as how we code."},{"time":73649,"text":"We have to ask questions, and hard questions,"},{"time":76747,"text":"to move past counting things"},{"time":78616,"text":"to understanding them."},{"time":81218,"text":"We're constantly bombarded with stories"},{"time":83664,"text":"about how much data there is in the world,"},{"time":86140,"text":"but when it comes to big data"},{"time":87720,"text":"and the challenges of interpreting it,"},{"time":90316,"text":"size isn't everything."},{"time":92404,"text":"There's also the speed at which it moves,"},{"time":95307,"text":"and the many varieties of data types,"},{"time":97003,"text":"and here are just a few examples:"},{"time":99501,"text":"images,"},{"time":101699,"text":"text,"},{"time":105706,"text":"video,"},{"time":107801,"text":"audio."},{"time":109631,"text":"And what unites this disparate types of data"},{"time":112673,"text":"is that they're created by people"},{"time":114894,"text":"and they require context."}]},{"cues":[{"time":117669,"text":"Now, there's a group of data scientists"},{"time":120114,"text":"out of the University of Illinois-Chicago,"},{"time":122419,"text":"and they're called the Health Media Collaboratory,"},{"time":124973,"text":"and they've been working with\nthe Centers for Disease Control"},{"time":127560,"text":"to better understand"},{"time":129065,"text":"how people talk about quitting smoking,"},{"time":131913,"text":"how they talk about electronic cigarettes,"},{"time":134593,"text":"and what they can do collectively"},{"time":136578,"text":"to help them quit."},{"time":138562,"text":"The interesting thing is, if you want to understand"},{"time":140575,"text":"how people talk about smoking,"},{"time":142791,"text":"first you have to understand"},{"time":144692,"text":"what they mean when they say \"smoking.\""},{"time":147257,"text":"And on Twitter, there are four main categories:"},{"time":151183,"text":"number one, smoking cigarettes;"},{"time":154180,"text":"number two, smoking marijuana;"},{"time":156987,"text":"number three, smoking ribs;"},{"time":159630,"text":"and number four, smoking hot women."},{"time":163183,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":166176,"text":"So then you have to think about, well,"},{"time":168602,"text":"how do people talk about electronic cigarettes?"},{"time":170742,"text":"And there are so many different ways"},{"time":172767,"text":"that people do this, and you can see from the slide"},{"time":175366,"text":"it's a complex kind of a query."},{"time":177976,"text":"And what it reminds us is that"},{"time":181200,"text":"language is created by people,"},{"time":183611,"text":"and people are messy and we're complex"},{"time":185951,"text":"and we use metaphors and slang and jargon"},{"time":188718,"text":"and we do this 24/7 in many, many languages,"},{"time":191997,"text":"and then as soon as we figure it out, we change it up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":195221,"text":"So did these ads that the CDC put on,"},{"time":200339,"text":"these television ads that featured a woman"},{"time":202769,"text":"with a hole in her throat and that were very graphic"},{"time":204790,"text":"and very disturbing,"},{"time":206694,"text":"did they actually have an impact"},{"time":208579,"text":"on whether people quit?"},{"time":211250,"text":"And the Health Media Collaboratory\nrespected the limits of their data,"},{"time":214557,"text":"but they were able to conclude"},{"time":216562,"text":"that those advertisements —\nand you may have seen them —"},{"time":219874,"text":"that they had the effect of jolting people"},{"time":222465,"text":"into a thought process"},{"time":224287,"text":"that may have an impact on future behavior."},{"time":227954,"text":"And what I admire and \nappreciate about this project,"},{"time":231845,"text":"aside from the fact, including the fact"},{"time":233334,"text":"that it's based on real human need,"},{"time":237391,"text":"is that it's a fantastic example of courage"},{"time":240237,"text":"in the face of a sea of irrelevance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":244680,"text":"And so it's not just big data that causes"},{"time":247985,"text":"challenges of interpretation, because let's face it,"},{"time":250586,"text":"we human beings have a very rich history"},{"time":253180,"text":"of taking any amount of data, no matter how small,"},{"time":255873,"text":"and screwing it up."},{"time":257490,"text":"So many years ago, you may remember"},{"time":261227,"text":"that former President Ronald Reagan"},{"time":263500,"text":"was very criticized for making a statement"},{"time":265491,"text":"that facts are stupid things."},{"time":268501,"text":"And it was a slip of the tongue, let's be fair."},{"time":271295,"text":"He actually meant to quote John Adams' defense"},{"time":273725,"text":"of British soldiers in the Boston Massacre trials"},{"time":276476,"text":"that facts are stubborn things."},{"time":279626,"text":"But I actually think there's"},{"time":282250,"text":"a bit of accidental wisdom in what he said,"},{"time":285668,"text":"because facts are stubborn things,"},{"time":288444,"text":"but sometimes they're stupid, too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":291367,"text":"I want to tell you a personal story"},{"time":293255,"text":"about why this matters a lot to me."},{"time":296803,"text":"I need to take a breath."},{"time":299240,"text":"My son Isaac, when he was two,"},{"time":301994,"text":"was diagnosed with autism,"},{"time":304411,"text":"and he was this happy, hilarious,"},{"time":306572,"text":"loving, affectionate little guy,"},{"time":308607,"text":"but the metrics on his developmental evaluations,"},{"time":311509,"text":"which looked at things like \nthe number of words —"},{"time":313579,"text":"at that point, none —"},{"time":317236,"text":"communicative gestures and minimal eye contact,"},{"time":321176,"text":"put his developmental level"},{"time":323179,"text":"at that of a nine-month-old baby."},{"time":327140,"text":"And the diagnosis was factually correct,"},{"time":330100,"text":"but it didn't tell the whole story."},{"time":333309,"text":"And about a year and a half later,"},{"time":334710,"text":"when he was almost four,"},{"time":336812,"text":"I found him in front of the computer one day"},{"time":339175,"text":"running a Google image search on women,"},{"time":344628,"text":"spelled \"w-i-m-e-n.\""},{"time":348244,"text":"And I did what any obsessed parent would do,"},{"time":350984,"text":"which is immediately started \nhitting the \"back\" button"},{"time":352885,"text":"to see what else he'd been searching for."},{"time":356248,"text":"And they were, in order: men,"},{"time":358419,"text":"school, bus and computer."},{"time":365686,"text":"And I was stunned,"},{"time":367756,"text":"because we didn't know that he could spell,"},{"time":369758,"text":"much less read, and so I asked him,"},{"time":371524,"text":"\"Isaac, how did you do this?\""},{"time":373717,"text":"And he looked at me very seriously and said,"},{"time":376395,"text":"\"Typed in the box.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":379747,"text":"He was teaching himself to communicate,"},{"time":383481,"text":"but we were looking in the wrong place,"},{"time":386485,"text":"and this is what happens when assessments"},{"time":388780,"text":"and analytics overvalue one metric —"},{"time":391176,"text":"in this case, verbal communication —"},{"time":393785,"text":"and undervalue others, such\nas creative problem-solving."},{"time":399488,"text":"Communication was hard for Isaac,"},{"time":401795,"text":"and so he found a workaround"},{"time":403707,"text":"to find out what he needed to know."},{"time":406564,"text":"And when you think about it, it makes a lot of sense,"},{"time":408454,"text":"because forming a question"},{"time":410535,"text":"is a really complex process,"},{"time":413100,"text":"but he could get himself a lot of the way there"},{"time":415622,"text":"by putting a word in a search box."}]},{"cues":[{"time":419714,"text":"And so this little moment"},{"time":422650,"text":"had a really profound impact on me"},{"time":425486,"text":"and our family"},{"time":426795,"text":"because it helped us change our frame of reference"},{"time":429936,"text":"for what was going on with him,"},{"time":432144,"text":"and worry a little bit less and appreciate"},{"time":435120,"text":"his resourcefulness more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":437302,"text":"Facts are stupid things."},{"time":440163,"text":"And they're vulnerable to misuse,"},{"time":442560,"text":"willful or otherwise."},{"time":444213,"text":"I have a friend, Emily Willingham, who's a scientist,"},{"time":447239,"text":"and she wrote a piece for Forbes not long ago"},{"time":450040,"text":"entitled \"The 10 Weirdest Things"},{"time":452020,"text":"Ever Linked to Autism.\""},{"time":453830,"text":"It's quite a list."},{"time":456835,"text":"The Internet, blamed for everything, right?"},{"time":460367,"text":"And of course mothers, because."},{"time":464124,"text":"And actually, wait, there's more,"},{"time":465711,"text":"there's a whole bunch in \nthe \"mother\" category here."},{"time":469141,"text":"And you can see it's a pretty \nrich and interesting list."},{"time":473956,"text":"I'm a big fan of"},{"time":476149,"text":"being pregnant near freeways, personally."},{"time":479853,"text":"The final one is interesting,"},{"time":481392,"text":"because the term \"refrigerator mother\""},{"time":484395,"text":"was actually the original hypothesis"},{"time":487000,"text":"for the cause of autism,"},{"time":488431,"text":"and that meant somebody \nwho was cold and unloving."}]},{"cues":[{"time":491166,"text":"And at this point, you might be thinking,"},{"time":492728,"text":"\"Okay, Susan, we get it,"},{"time":494385,"text":"you can take data, you can \nmake it mean anything.\""},{"time":496167,"text":"And this is true, it's absolutely true,"},{"time":500870,"text":"but the challenge is that"},{"time":506480,"text":"we have this opportunity"},{"time":508928,"text":"to try to make meaning out of it ourselves,"},{"time":511212,"text":"because frankly, data doesn't \ncreate meaning. We do."},{"time":516564,"text":"So as businesspeople, as consumers,"},{"time":519820,"text":"as patients, as citizens,"},{"time":522359,"text":"we have a responsibility, I think,"},{"time":524755,"text":"to spend more time"},{"time":526949,"text":"focusing on our critical thinking skills."},{"time":529819,"text":"Why?"},{"time":530897,"text":"Because at this point in our history, as we've heard"},{"time":534075,"text":"many times over,"},{"time":535781,"text":"we can process exabytes of data"},{"time":537762,"text":"at lightning speed,"},{"time":539915,"text":"and we have the potential to make bad decisions"},{"time":543430,"text":"far more quickly, efficiently,"},{"time":545264,"text":"and with far greater impact than we did in the past."},{"time":550292,"text":"Great, right?"},{"time":551680,"text":"And so what we need to do instead"},{"time":554710,"text":"is spend a little bit more time"},{"time":557040,"text":"on things like the humanities"},{"time":559786,"text":"and sociology, and the social sciences,"},{"time":563250,"text":"rhetoric, philosophy, ethics,"},{"time":565558,"text":"because they give us context that is so important"},{"time":568414,"text":"for big data, and because"},{"time":570990,"text":"they help us become better critical thinkers."},{"time":573408,"text":"Because after all, if I can spot"},{"time":577615,"text":"a problem in an argument, it doesn't much matter"},{"time":580101,"text":"whether it's expressed in words or in numbers."},{"time":582860,"text":"And this means"},{"time":585579,"text":"teaching ourselves to find \nthose confirmation biases"},{"time":590000,"text":"and false correlations"},{"time":591822,"text":"and being able to spot a naked emotional appeal"},{"time":593960,"text":"from 30 yards,"},{"time":595622,"text":"because something that happens after something"},{"time":598144,"text":"doesn't mean it happened \nbecause of it, necessarily,"},{"time":601226,"text":"and if you'll let me geek out on you for a second,"},{"time":603345,"text":"the Romans called this \n\"post hoc ergo propter hoc,\""},{"time":607642,"text":"after which therefore because of which."}]},{"cues":[{"time":610938,"text":"And it means questioning\ndisciplines like demographics."},{"time":614695,"text":"Why? Because they're based on assumptions"},{"time":617215,"text":"about who we all are based on our gender"},{"time":619521,"text":"and our age and where we live"},{"time":620983,"text":"as opposed to data on what \nwe actually think and do."},{"time":624461,"text":"And since we have this data,"},{"time":626124,"text":"we need to treat it with appropriate privacy controls"},{"time":629263,"text":"and consumer opt-in,"},{"time":632839,"text":"and beyond that, we need to be clear"},{"time":635832,"text":"about our hypotheses,"},{"time":637935,"text":"the methodologies that we use,"},{"time":640531,"text":"and our confidence in the result."},{"time":643335,"text":"As my high school algebra teacher used to say,"},{"time":645809,"text":"show your math,"},{"time":647340,"text":"because if I don't know what steps you took,"},{"time":650781,"text":"I don't know what steps you didn't take,"},{"time":652772,"text":"and if I don't know what questions you asked,"},{"time":655210,"text":"I don't know what questions you didn't ask."},{"time":658407,"text":"And it means asking ourselves, really,"},{"time":659930,"text":"the hardest question of all:"},{"time":661409,"text":"Did the data really show us this,"},{"time":664909,"text":"or does the result make us feel"},{"time":667220,"text":"more successful and more comfortable?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":671098,"text":"So the Health Media Collaboratory,"},{"time":673682,"text":"at the end of their project, they were able"},{"time":675381,"text":"to find that 87 percent of tweets"},{"time":678789,"text":"about those very graphic and disturbing"},{"time":680933,"text":"anti-smoking ads expressed fear,"},{"time":684971,"text":"but did they conclude"},{"time":686827,"text":"that they actually made people stop smoking?"},{"time":689988,"text":"No. It's science, not magic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":692530,"text":"So if we are to unlock"},{"time":695720,"text":"the power of data,"},{"time":698582,"text":"we don't have to go blindly into"},{"time":702030,"text":"Orwell's vision of a totalitarian future,"},{"time":705466,"text":"or Huxley's vision of a trivial one,"},{"time":708583,"text":"or some horrible cocktail of both."},{"time":711603,"text":"What we have to do"},{"time":713982,"text":"is treat critical thinking with respect"},{"time":716700,"text":"and be inspired by examples"},{"time":718729,"text":"like the Health Media Collaboratory,"},{"time":721339,"text":"and as they say in the superhero movies,"},{"time":723667,"text":"let's use our powers for good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":725489,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":727840,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}